{
  "stem": "9728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went back to-- to Lodz again in '46.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again I spent about 14 days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't find anybody alive from my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said goodbye.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I thought I'll never going to come back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I smuggled myself back to Eastern Germany, back to Munich, because I knew that if I want to go any place I have to go from Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I lived in Germany '46 til '47.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In '48, I decided that I will go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "While I was in-- while I lived in Munich, I worked at the Jewish committee in Munich.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in 1948, I decided I will go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By the end of 1948, you have to realize that Israel was just came to-- into existence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When I came to Israel straight from the ship, they took me from the ship that I arrived, and they put me into a boot camp-- into a military camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was not my choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I can realize now, and I can appreciate, they had to have all the abled men to the military, because it was either there is going to be a nation or not.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I were in the service close to two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I did not see any fighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on the border, on the border, on the Syrian border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was on the border of Jordan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few words, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to-- you have to know a little bit Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in-- in the outskirt of Sembach, I believe, it was the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in Israel close to two years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I stayed [LAUGHS] in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
